1. apollo folder contains the angular code
2. The gql-server folder contains the express-node server code
3. The first two task are there under the src/app directory structure with list and middleware folder. the server2.js in the gql-server contains the server for task2.
4. The third task is there under paginator folder
5. The fourth task is there in the display folder
6. Please run the angular code on the browser from navigation - Assignment1 -> Assignment2 => Assignment 3. 
7. Once you click on any title on Assignment 3, then the details of that component is display on browser. 

